    Note over Orchestrator,Detector: Flow 1: PII Detection Request

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: None
    Note right of Detector: JSON Body:<br/>{"contents": ["text..."],<br/>"detector_params":<br/>{"regex": ["ssn","email",<br/>"credit-card"]}}

    Detector->>Detectors: Match text against<br/>built-in patterns<br/>(email, SSN, credit-card)
    Detectors-->>Detector: Detection results<br/>(start, end, text,<br/>detection_type, score)

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>JSON detection results<br/>HTTP (plaintext)

    Note over Kubelet,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    Kubelet->>Detector: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (plaintext)<br/>Auth: None
    Detector-->>Kubelet: 200 OK "healthy"

    Note over Orchestrator,Detectors: No egress connections<br/>All processing is in-memory<br/>Service is fully stateless
